        <div n="X84A723L" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-1"> In sounds of Ioys your tunefull Voices raise&#13;</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-2"> And teach the People whom to thank &amp; praise.</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-3"> Thank Prudent Zoras providential Reign,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-4"> For Peace &amp; Plenty &amp; all sorts of Grain.</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-5"> Thank the Stock-jobbers for your thriving Trade,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-6"> Thank just Go.n that all Debts are paid.</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-7"> Thank the Scots P--rs for firm &amp; unbought Union.</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-8"> Thank B.ps for Occasional Communion.</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-9"> Thank Ma--ghs Zeal, who scorn'd the profer'd Treaty,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-10"> And thank Eugene the French did not beat ye.</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-11"> Thank Whigs that vote the Church need fear no Ruin,</l><l n="12" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-12"> As plain appears by what those Whigs are doing.</l><l n="13" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-13"> Thank your ownselvs that you're so taxt &amp; shamm'd,</l><l n="14" xml:id="spp-X84A723L-line-14"> But thank th'Almighty that you are not damn'd.X84A723L   </l></lg></div>
